metadata.title: Senate offers Fateha for Armed Forces personnel, flood victims

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Oct 09 (APP):The Senate on Thursday offered 'Fateha' for Shaheed Lt Col Junaid Tariq, Major Tayyab Rahat, Major Sibtain Haider and other personnel of Armed Forces who embraced martyrdom in operations against Indian proxy Khwarij in Orakzai The House also offered Fateha for civilians who lost their lives in recent floods and other incidents. The Fateha was led by Noorul Haq Qadri on the request of Acting Chairman Senate Syedaal Khan Nasar.
